import Axios from 'axios'
import React from 'react'

const RegisterPage = () =>{
    return <tr>
        <th><input type="text" className="form-control" placeholder="username" /></th>
        <th><input type="text" className="form-control" placeholder="email" /></th>
        <th><input type="text" className="form-control" placeholder="password" /></th>
        <th><input type="text" className="form-control" placeholder="confirmation password" /></th>
        <th><button type="button" className="btn btn-outline-warning"></button></th>
    </tr>
}
